data.description: Features of this open floor plan home include a nice sized kitchen with cherry cabinets and a stainless-steel refrigerator and microwave.  Separate seating area/dining room.  First floor laundry plus powder room and spacious living room with ceiling fan completes the first floor.  Upstairs, you will find the vaulted primary bedroom with a private full bath and walk-in closet, the second bedroom, another full bath, plus a large loft that could be converted to a third bedroom.  All upstairs rooms have lighted ceiling fans.  All appliances are included.  A private fenced backyard and 2-car garage complete this move-in ready home.  Sold as-is, with fast close possible.  The community features a park and playground area.
